metadata.name: ApeRock Vol. 1
metadata.description:
BURN COMING!  
Apes are exploring and discovering new worlds as they fly through the galaxy. Always accompanying them is 'Ape Rock Vol.1', a top chart album known galaxywide.  
On an unknown planet, the apes discovered a long-lost music album, "Vol. 2," including top songs such as "You Aped in All Night Long," "Billy Ape," and "Hotel Apetown." Keep your copies of Vol. 1 close. You may soon need to burn them in order to acquire Vol. 2 & physical merchandise in the next stage. (The burn mechanism will be explained in detail soon).
